<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>78</hymn_number>
<title>Sioshwi Dhambi zangu TZR78</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Sioshwi dhambi zangu,
 Bila damu yake Yesu.
 Hapendezewi Mungu,
 Bila damu yake Yesu.

[V2]
 Hakuna kabisa
 Dawa ya makosa
 Ya kututakasa,
 Ila damu yake Yesu.

[V3]
 La kunisafi sina
 Ila damu yake Yesu.
 Wala udhuru tena,
 Ila damu yake Yesu.

[V4]
 Sipati pataniswa,
 Bila damu yake Yesu.
 Hukumu yanitisha,
 Bila damu yake Yesu.

[V5]
 Sipati tumaini,
 Bila damu yake Yesu.
 Wema wala amani,
 Bila damu yake Yesu.

[V6]
 Yashinda ulimwengu,
 Hiyo damu yake Yesu.
 Na kutufikisha juu,
 Hiyo damu yake Yesu.

[V7]
 Twaimba: Utukufu
 Una damu yake Yesu.
 Milele twaisifu,
 Hiyo damu yake Yesu.</lyrics>
</song>